minnaram ( english : lighthouse / beacon ) is a 1994 indian malayalam musical romantic drama film written and directed by priyadarshan from a story by cheriyan kalpakavadi .   the film stars mohanlal , shobana , thilakan , sankaradi , k. p. ummer , jagathy sreekumar , geetha vijayan , venu nagavally , and lalu alex. it was produced by r. mohan for goodknight films .